## Imperium Store Visual Palette

Direction: pristine federal fintech. The store should feel official, quiet, precise, and premium. Cyan is no longer the dominant brand color. It becomes a small technical/data accent for the Option Trading Terminal. Federal blue carries the store identity. Gold carries premium value and the Imperium Investor cue.

