## Final Direction

The store should read as:

```text
official federal blue base
+ black navy depth
+ clear white typography
+ small gold premium signals
+ tiny cyan technical data details
```

The important shift is restraint. The product screenshots already contain strong identity. The store interface should frame them cleanly instead of competing with them.
